Description:
The geography of this island is unique. There is a big crater that covers the majority of the island. 

Sigrun points out the best approach to the island, noting that it is a good place to replenish the ship's supplies. 

She also mentions that she would like to retrieve something from the island, indicating that she knows this place very well.
